Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:45.86,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lonely night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:47.80,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting back again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:51.96,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to be like it never ends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.24,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give us hope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:54.38,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,through the love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:55.74,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or feels more
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:00.06,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,shine on me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.16,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強く降り止まぬ雨に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:17.07,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔忘れたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:22.07,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦しむすれ違う世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:29.56,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争いと偽りの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:36.50,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心枯らすのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.71,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒れ狂う波
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:43.68,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮かぶ花のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:51.16,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lead the way 嵐を乗り越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:58.52,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涸れゆく大地を潤しえるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:09.10,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO AHEAD 真っすく歩み出せる？

Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:45.86,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤寂长夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:47.80,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又再度降临
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:51.96,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛没有止境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.24,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从爱里面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:54.38,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:55.74,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:00.06,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感同身受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.16,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知停歇的暴雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:17.07,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我在痛苦中忘却了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:22.07,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在交错的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:29.56,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了纷争与虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:36.50,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人心枯竭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.71,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂暴的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:43.68,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像花朵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:51.16,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lead the way 跨越难关
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:58.52,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像滋润渐渐干涸的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:09.10,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO AHEAD 我是否能笔直前进？






